{"tid":1289961,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"屯公啲人玩夠膠未？","createTime":"2019-07-06T10:11:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-06T13:47:43.000Z","uid":132227,"like":1,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4721c27bb9a5bd9d3d2caceac677e0a69f71766d","tid":1289961,"uid":132227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T10:11:01.000Z","msg":"乜撚嘢一個都不能少<br />\n將依句同烈士講既口號去同隻大陸雞講<br />\n四個烈士泉下有知真係彈番上黎屌鳩你地<br />\n<br />\n而且咁大動員力去圍個公廁係冇意義<br />\n黑警仆街、冇腦已經唔係新鮮事<br />\n你繼續focus落去不如用依個人數做更有意義既事啦<br />\n<br />\n雖然話兄弟爬山唔好分化<br />\n以上說話亦可能唔合你意<br />\n但都唔該大家諗清楚目標同綱領<br />\n唔好柴娃娃貪得意好玩咁做啲消耗民意、體力又冇意義既on9行為 感謝"},{"pid":"9ea18f2e869e2e49ef940c08d6ab6f01f7d26aa6","tid":1289961,"uid":102343,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T10:12:39.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n<br />\n屯公針對番保皇區議員會唔會好d?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1289906\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1289906</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1e61f47399bf5a511d29a1939dd0eb7d74643c53","tid":1289961,"uid":119145,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T10:13:03.000Z","msg":"樓主你唔係住屯門我唔怪你"},{"pid":"fa0239e0359d16c3257a34b7e3f88b65c26ad733","tid":1289961,"uid":33495,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T10:16:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KfMyKOp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKfMyKOp.png&h=68360e20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n養好啲個account先啦垃撚圾<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88339a891e94380fbf3e89ce4547bf375d5ada0d","tid":1289961,"uid":104397,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T10:20:50.000Z","msg":"屯門牛牛發洩到咪得囉<br />\n雖然我係九龍人都走過去支持下<br />\n佢地又唔係破壞又唔係打人<br />\n派下膠幽默下幾好丫<br />\n我又覺得無分散個注意喎<br />\n屯門既事都關香港人事囉<br />\n<br />\n昨日旺角，今日屯門，明日可能係你屋企樓下"},{"pid":"90ece9194ba0bb6691e08238c80c146cc19ef421","tid":1289961,"uid":268217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T10:22:02.000Z","msg":"咁應該去邊同做咩？"},{"pid":"c1b958be197557480655a83e82e2ec8a3662823c","tid":1289961,"uid":77242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T10:25:50.000Z","msg":"樓主錯唔晒嘅其實"},{"pid":"52987dc3e3334b2ec5ce80627e2f68f8bb2f792b","tid":1289961,"uid":132227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90ece9194ba0bb6691e08238c80c146cc19ef421","tid":1289961,"uid":268217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T10:22:02.000Z","msg":"咁應該去邊同做咩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T10:28:16.000Z","msg":"要求議員關注<br />\n人地今日避風頭 之後繼續出黎唱歌派利是<br />\n行動不外乎都係發夢和理非會做既嘢<br />\n廢寧以言入罪唔講咁詳細 自己諗 都係基本嘢"},{"pid":"c10eb7089b2a1c00e8e24c5003ae5997c4b795f2","tid":1289961,"uid":132227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T10:28:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁應該去邊同做咩？</blockquote>要求議員關注<br />\n人地今日避風頭 之後繼續出黎唱歌派利是<br />\n行動不外乎都係發夢和理非會做既嘢<br />\n廢<span style=\"color: red;\">事</span>以言入罪唔講咁詳細 自己諗 都係基本嘢</blockquote>"},{"pid":"78b025d2a6cd21994d214bc2aaada56f747d0c26","tid":1289961,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T13:47:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}